{"tid":1459060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺有樣野我地點都唔夠班藍絲鬥？？？？？","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:12:31.000Z","uid":25168,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"206cf341fee7df76e75a108e26e843aa56a0e402","tid":1459060,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"就係鬥無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n射爆女仔既眼單野<br />\n入藍絲page係全部一律拍手叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信如果有示威者比警察殺左<br />\n佢地都係大大聲讚警隊做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMH7A1O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMH7A1O.png&h=a80fabca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkP2pU8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkP2pU8.png&h=5286622a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b8ab70bb4af0c9f28fd0b7d27940ab4f9cb0f08","tid":1459060,"uid":25168,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"有時玩下火都大把黃絲係度叫 阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有示威者殺撚左個警案 相信大把&rsquo;自己人&lsquo;篤佢出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">「警察係唔岩 但xxx就太過份啦？」</span><br />\n呢句野相信大家都聽唔少人講<br />\n但有無聽過藍絲話<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">「示威者係唔岩 但xxx就太過份啦？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無。因為佢地已經無良心 <br />\n其實佢地既無限支持警隊 係好值得我地學習<br />\n無論點都不割蓆方面 佢地做得好出色</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd168724ff32442147be5d7615f3401abf556af1","tid":1459060,"uid":25168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"不過就係無良心先會做藍絲<br />\n有良心先會撐雞蛋呢面<br />\n<br />\n如果我地完全無良心又會變做藍絲<br />\n如果藍絲有返少少良心又會變做黃<br />\n所以呢個真係死局黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c26949fb958442014b53c87ebeb85b46ff41aa","tid":1459060,"uid":170772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"調轉唸 如果有狗俾手中打死<br />\n我相信連登熱門兩日都係慶祝po"},{"pid":"e434230feff7b2b0a120379fce02ca02c7ec448d","tid":1459060,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"ff317dd6c37b88cb67699b47aac12bed7cfbb8bd","tid":1459060,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9efa33b529c2423c2ec0e0f20c055c857b09a806","tid":1459060,"uid":25168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"仲有樣野就係<br />\n藍絲既無腦都係佢地咁&rsquo;團結&lsquo;既原因<br />\n今日大把藍絲係度瘋傳呢張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GR7O4WP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGR7O4WP.jpg&h=1f10a44a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔會有藍絲嗌fact check/用下個腦諗下<br />\n見到有利自己果面既就會瘋傳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後見到有人改左篇野<br />\n入面全部留言都係嗌fact check/同屌9佢做假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0PRHpXD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PRHpXD.png&h=a4a059db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUfAKXE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUfAKXE.png&h=569d204c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGjYHKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGjYHKk.png&h=ac5687ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話 無腦都係藍絲們既致勝關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3be500487b44b22e4e2fdec58a3075009677e49","tid":1459060,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"sorry借位跪求推<br />\n突發！ 點解冇人講816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"63e4b5336c053f38232552c6b8aeb3e38e076e0e","tid":1459060,"uid":15362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"無腦+無良心=藍絲 <br />\n 支持警察=支持南京大屠殺"},{"pid":"ef6a9b5c11b4241de35c5535d650e8be4aa2b9a1","tid":1459060,"uid":9214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"人地就算係fake news對自己放有利嘅都撐左先<br />\n<br />\n我地樣樣野都要fact check 再慢慢澄清<br />\n點夠人玩呀"},{"pid":"6e8cf98f44c86f9d0cf2f3aded8e519e6723751e","tid":1459060,"uid":25168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"不過都係果句<br />\n有腦就唔做藍絲啦<br />\n<br />\n所以都係死局黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db97c6722efd4a2b619f8fe8e5e6b69cd9d77ca","tid":1459060,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"其實係立場問題，共狗死連登仔都笑得好仆街"},{"pid":"e63c0842075c79e95065ae8edeca966e0104538d","tid":1459060,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"佢地班人係堅無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe3148d6033c401a7c74573f184d80dfb71c396","tid":1459060,"uid":190962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"【定期提醒】再咁搞法場運動好快完（唔該睇唒！）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"75302068ceccd34c5ba5cfcefca3eeb76b6891d4","tid":1459060,"uid":25168,"li